{"tid":2302001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張祺忠好友感歎：佢衰就衰在成日唔識講「No」","createTime":"2020-11-26T19:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:41:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":187,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"373bc68ba7d3727a86522079b561bbd3b2256f3b","tid":2302001,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"「其實佢個人nice到不得了，所以呢單嘢咁樣就冇人會相信嘅。」與張祺忠相識半世紀的陳梁材，擔任辯方證人，作供後在庭外續談本案，憶述最初以為案件是假新聞，兩年來一直支持身處牢中的張祺忠。陳透露張現今精神不俗，在獄中幫忙計計數，做業餘興趣研究；不過從容背後也許有點裝作堅強，避免朋友擔心，「佢衰就衰在成日唔識講no㗎&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/TKEEYCHHZ5FHFP2KYQ6E4IIJ2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2FTKEEYCHHZ5FHFP2KYQ6E4IIJ2A%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=93aefa61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2FTKEEYCHHZ5FHFP2KYQ6E4IIJ2A%2F&h=908b598a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/TKEEYCHHZ5FHFP2KYQ6E4IIJ2A/</a>"},{"pid":"07ce30f5369386f745a455a0f7e94fa72046a929","tid":2302001,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962cd6dc2b95022c5f4cecba786ea13ce15b41ab","tid":2302001,"uid":16676,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T19:12:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/3/1490723317_dm-1280w.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F3%2F1490723317_dm-1280w.jpg&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=b1f53177\" target=\"_blank\">https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/3/1490723317_dm-1280w.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n林生都好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/face